answers.body_markdown:
After Adding @path  I solved my problem like this

  @GET(&quot;/payment/fetch/board/{username}&quot;)
    Call&lt;List&lt;BoardResponse&gt;&gt;fetchBoardList(@Path(&quot;username&quot;) String username);

in the retrofit API interface, you should add @Path before username parameter  like this 

```
@GET(&quot;/payment/fetch/board/{username}&quot;)
Call&lt;List&lt;BoardResponse&gt;&gt;fetchBoardList(@Path(&quot;username&quot;) String username);
```

